{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/pulls/12584", "id": 3066049707, "node_id": "PR_kwDOBXYo-M62wDSr", "html_url": "https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade/pull/12584", "diff_url": "https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade/pull/12584.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade/pull/12584.patch", "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/issues/12584", "number": 12584, "state": "closed", "locked": false, "title": "Hyperliquid HIP3 support", "user": {"login": "igi01", "id": 88946458, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg4OTQ2NDU4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/88946458?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01", "html_url": "https://github.com/igi01", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/igi01/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "body": "## Foreword\r\nThank you for your previous feedback. I’ve started over cleanly once again and hope that it now comes closer to the expectations. Sorry, I’m still gaining my first experiences. I wanted to tackle the problem on my own and ended up finding a solution that works for me, which i wanted to share. If this ends up creating more work than it’s worth, or causes frustration due to poor code quality, please feel free to simply ignore or decline it.\r\n\r\n## Tests & Code Style\r\n\r\nPEP8 compliance is ensured via existing pre-commit hooks (ruff, flake8, mypy)\r\nComplete Unit Test passed for the new files \r\n\r\n## AI Usage Declaration\r\n\r\nYes, parts of this PR were created with the assistance of AI (Claude Sonnet 3.5), followed by manual review, testing, and validation.\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\nFix missing wallet balances for HIP-3 assets on Hyperliquid.\r\n\r\nSolve the issue: #12558\r\n\r\n## Quick changelog\r\n\r\n-Add support for HIP-3 DEX assets in the Hyperliquid wallet integration\r\n-Ensure correct balance and position detection for HIP-3  assets\r\n-Prevent false \"Not enough balance\" errors on trade exit\r\n-Make HIP-3 detection fully optional via config (exchange.hip3_dexes)\r\n-Add compatibility for multiple and future HIP-3 perpetual DEXes\r\n-Add strict config validation for hip3_dexes\r\n\r\n## What's new?\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes an issue where HIP-3 assets on Hyperliquid were not properly detected by the wallet system in Freqtrade.\r\nPreviously, positions were opened and shown correctly by the exchange, but the internal wallet failed to recognize HIP-3 token balances. This resulted in false warnings like:\r\n\"Not enough balance in wallet to exit trade\"\r\n\r\n**With this change:**\r\nHIP-3 assets are now correctly resolved and displayed in the wallet\r\nExisting positions can be exited without false insufficient balance errors\r\nNo behavior change for non-HIP-3 assets\r\n\r\n**Configuration & performance behavior**\r\nHIP-3 support is fully opt-in and only active when configured explicitly.\r\n**Example configuration:**\r\n```\r\n    \"exchange\": {\r\n        \"name\": \"hyperliquid\",\r\n        \"hip3_dexes\": [\"xyz\",\"vntl\",...],\r\n```\r\nAdditional API calls are only executed if exchange.hip3_dexes is set.\r\n\r\n**This guarantees:**\r\nZero overhead for standard Hyperliquid users\r\nNo additional rate-limit usage unless HIP-3 is enabled\r\nClean separation between default behavior and HIP-3 extensions\r\n\r\n**Configuration validation**\r\nThis PR adds a strict config validation rule to prevent misconfiguration:\r\nThe exchange.hip3_dexes parameter is only allowed if the selected exchange is \"hyperliquid\"\r\nUsing hip3_dexes with any other exchange will raise a ConfigurationError\r\nThis ensures that HIP-3 specific settings cannot be accidentally enabled for unsupported exchanges.\r\n\r\n**Future compatibility**\r\nThe implementation is designed to be:\r\nCompatible with multiple HIP-3 perpetual DEXes\r\nForward-compatible with future HIP-3 DEX additions\r\nIndependent of any single HIP-3 market", "created_at": "2025-12-03T06:10:45Z", "updated_at": "2025-12-30T20:03:24Z", "closed_at": "2025-12-30T20:03:14Z", "merged_at": "2025-12-30T20:03:13Z", "merge_commit_sha": "8e91fea11f3cc0354b952a5b667628b18378c7fe", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [{"id": 9004572807, "node_id": "LA_kwDOBXYo-M8AAAACGLbghw", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/labels/AI%20Slop", "name": "AI Slop", "color": "1ce0bb", "default": false, "description": "Issue or PR partially or completely generated by AI"}], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/pulls/12584/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/pulls/12584/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/issues/12584/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/freqtrade/freqtrade/statuses/0f8c6d456e36d0b732883577534cda6630465398", "head": {"label": "igi01:feature/hyperliquid-hip3-support", "ref": "feature/hyperliquid-hip3-support", "sha": "0f8c6d456e36d0b732883577534cda6630465398", "user": {"login": "igi01", "id": 88946458, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg4OTQ2NDU4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/88946458?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users